Module com.example.bankingtransactionsgui
Package com.example.bank

Class Date

java.lang.Object
com.example.bank.Date
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.lang.Comparable<Date>
public class Date
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<Date>
The class is used to make the date for the profile class information. We get the date from the user or have a default date constructor if none are received. Initialize all variables, year, month, and day to create the Date object. Implement methods to manipulate Date object.
Author:
Akshat Mehta and Atharva Patil
